## Production bug fixed this session

**LogRecord 'name' overwrite** (fa7e1872): 13 production files in
packages/kailash-dataflow/src/dataflow/ passed `extra={"name": <value>}`
to `logger.info/error/debug`. Python logging reserves `name` for the
logger name and raises `KeyError: "Attempt to overwrite 'name' in
