crashed at runtime.

Renamed keys to context-specific names (column_name, migration_name,
database_name, gateway_name, phase_name, class_name, savepoint_name,
pool_name, pattern_name, check_name). Scanned root SDK + all other
sub-packages — no other sites affected.

